<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="inserting-local-xref" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Inserting Local Xref</title>
  <taskbody>
    <context>
      <p id="insert-local-xref-intro">You can insert an xref to a local target.</p>
      <p>Do the following:</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Call up the <uicontrol>Insert Local Xref Dialog</uicontrol>. </cmd>
        <info>
          <p>To call up the <keyword>Insert Local Xref Dialog</keyword>, choose <menucascade>
              <uicontrol>DITA</uicontrol>
              <uicontrol>Insert Local Xref</uicontrol>
            </menucascade> or click the <uicontrol>Insert Local Xref</uicontrol> button <image href="insert-local-xreference-button.png" align="center"/> on the toolbar.</p>
        </info>
        <stepresult>
          <p>The <keyword>Insert Local Xref Dialog</keyword> will appear.</p>
          <fig>
            <title>Insert Local Xref Dialog.</title>
            <image href="insert-local-xref-dialog.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
          </fig>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Select the target.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>In the <uicontrol>Insert Local Xref Dialog</uicontrol>, select the target from the <uicontrol>Targets</uicontrol> list.</p>
          <image href="insert-local-xref-dialog-target-selected.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
          <p><note id="note-targets">
              <p>You can see the list of available targets in the current document.</p>
              <p>To filter the targets by type, select a type from the <uicontrol>Show types</uicontrol> drop-down list.</p>
            </note><image href="show-types-list-local-xref.png" align="center" placement="break"/></p>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Insert</uicontrol> button to insert the local xref.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step-close-dialog">
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Close</uicontrol> button to close the dialog.</cmd>
        <info>
          <note>
            <p>You can also  check the <uicontrol>Close on Insert</uicontrol> checkbox, and then click the <uicontrol>Insert</uicontrol> button. </p>
          </note>
        </info>
      </step>
    </steps>
    <result>
      <fig frame="all">
        <title>Local xref inserted.</title>
        <image href="local-xref-inserted.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
      </fig>
    </result>
  </taskbody>
</task>
